title: New Guinea - lessons from a cradle of agriculture and languages

media:group.media:title: New Guinea - lessons from a cradle of agriculture and languages
media:group.media:description:
This island is home to bananas, sugarcane and more languages than anywhere else. Watch how words, crops and people connect in a place now known to be an original cradle of agriculture.

Aid: https://docs.google.com/document/d/1ywiOfzN5FZt2sh7s3V8EfCB54vUoHg4iA1VevAxgZeU/#heading=h.8iwaseaw0ce6
